text: A.S.D. Junior Biellese Libertas is a football club which plays to Biella in Italy. The club in season 2010-11, in Promozione is promoted in Eccellenza Piemonte. The colors of the team are black and white. == References == Category:Italian football clubs Category:Province of Biella Category:1902 establishments in Italy
